Package: mcrl
Version: 1.3.0
Section: games
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: default-jre | java-runtime
Maintainer: Sm0keSkreen
Homepage: https://github.com/Sm0keSkreen/mcrl
Description: Lift Minecraft's account chat restriction across every loader/version
 JVM javaagent that lifts Minecraft's account chat restriction, applied globally
 via JDK_JAVA_OPTIONS so it works across vanilla and every loader (Fabric, Forge,
 Quilt, NeoForge) without per-instance setup.
